high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the dishwasher, then turn to the counter on your right, that the microwave sits on.
Pick up the knife, behind the paper towels, on the counter.
Turn around and go to the round, black table, across the kitchen.
Cut the potato, in front of the plant, on the table, into slices.
Turn around and go across the kitchen to the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and go back to the round table across the room.
Pick up one of the potato slices, on the table.
Turn to your right and go to the refrigerator.
Place the potato slice on the shelf above the drawers, in the refrigerator, wait a moment for the potato slice to chill, then remove the potato slice from the refrigerator.
Turn to your right and walk back to the microwave, across the kitchen.
Place the potato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato slice in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the dishwasher then turn right to face the counter with the paper towels on it.
Pick up the knife on the counter behind the paper towels.
Turn around and walk to the round table behind you.
Cut the potato on the table.
Turn around and walk to the microwave on the counter.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the round table.
Pick up a potato slice from the table.
Turn right and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the potato inside the fridge then shut the door, open the door and get the potato.
Turn around then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Put the potato inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife and the potato slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and cross the room, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the kitchen table.
Cut the potato on the kitchen table into slices.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the kitchen table.
Pick up a slice of the potato on the kitchen table.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Cool the potato slice in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Place the potato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: TO cool a potato slice and place it in the microwave.
